title: Search underway for missing 14-year-old boy
text:
Fabian Szafarczyk Police are appealing for help to find a missing teenager who was last seen at his home in Perry Barr on Wednesday 8th February.
Fabian Szafarczyk is white, 6ft tall, with short black hair and was last seen wearing a black jacket, black jeans and white trainers.
It's thought the 14-year-old - who has been missing before - was thinking of travelling to Newcastle.
Anyone with information can call the Locate team on 101.
 West Midlands Perry Barr Birmingham
